38 Sec. 11. 38 MRSA §2146, sub-§6, ¶A is enacted to read:
39 A. Notwithstanding any provision of this section to the contrary, a producer may not
40 be required to pay an increased fee or penalty for packaging material that is not
41 composed of post-consumer recycled material if the packaging material is subject to
42 state or federal laws, rules or regulations that effectively prohibit the use of post-
43 consumer recycled material in that packaging material.
